Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Unrivaled industrial location. Central Kewdale location 	providing close and convenient access to Perth Road network including Abernethy Road and Roe and Tonkin Highways.

Location Features:
- Perth airport: 1km*
- Kewdale Freight Terminal: 2.5km*
- Abernethy Road: 500m*
- Tonkin Highway: 750m*
- Roe Highway: 4km*

Key Features:
- Highly felxible warehousing providing areas 					from 5,000sqm* - 12,000sqm*
- 2 street frontages providing drive-thru and drive-around 				flexibility with surlpus laydown
- Proposed ESFR fire sprinkler system
- Ability to upgrade or modify existing building to suit tenant 			operation requirements
